title: Vanity Fair Confidential - Season 1
description:
Vanity Fair Confidential - Season 1

Vanity Fair Confidential brings you deep into the criminal affairs of various people whose stories were once across the pages of Vanity Fair Magazine. The show covers high scandal cases including those of soldiers, family heirs, and even boy band moguls.

Ep 1 - The Runaway Doctor
Ep 2 - The Fugitive Heir
Ep 3 - Prisoner Of Denver
Ep 4 - The Lady Vanishes
Ep 5 - The Case Of The Vanishing Blonde
Ep 6 - The Counterfeit Rockefeller
Ep 7 - Don't Ask Don't Kill
Ep 8 - Alter Ego
Ep 9 - Mad About The Boys
Ep 10 - Legend With A Bullet
Ep 11 - The White House Boys
Ep 12 - Presumed Guilty
